    "content": "[Intro]\r\nN.C.\r\nHow are the tenders, Johnny?\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\nN.C.\r\nWhy don't you ask him if he's going to stay?\r\nN.C.\r\nWhy don't you ask him if he's going away?\r\nN.C.\r\nWhy don't you tell me what's going on?\r\nN.C.\r\nWhy don't you tell me who's on the phone?\r\n\r\n\r\n(Bass Comes In At 1:09)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-2h4p0---0-0-----0-0-----0---0-----0-----|\r\nA|-------2-----0h3-----0-3---3---0-3---3---|\r\nE|-----------------------------------------|x2[/tab]\r\n\r\nWhy don't you ask him what's going wrong?\r\nWhy don't you ask him who's the latest on his throne?\r\n(Ooga-aga-ooga)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-2h4p0---0-0-----0-0-----0---0-----0-----|\r\nA|-------2-----0h3-----0-3---3---0-3---3---|\r\nE|-----------------------------------------|x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Bridge]\r\n(1:55)\r\n\r\nDon't say that you love me (Hiyee)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x4[/tab]\r\n\r\nJust tell me that you want me (Hiyee)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x3[/tab]\r\n\r\nTusk!\r\n\r\n\r\nJust say that you want me (Hiyee)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x4[/tab]\r\n\r\nDon't tell me that you--\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Outro]\r\n\r\nTusk! (Real savage-like)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x8[/tab]\r\n\r\nTusk!\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x4[/tab]\r\n\r\nTusk!\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x4[/tab]\r\n\r\nTusk! Tusk! Tusk!\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-2-2---2----|\r\nD|-----4---0--|\r\nA|------------|\r\nE|------------|x6[/tab]\r\n\r\n(Fade)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n***********************************\r\n\r\n|h  